         |
         v
drf-spectacular (schema generation)
         |
         v
/api/schema/ (OpenAPI 3.0 JSON/YAML)
         |
         v
orval (code generation)
         |
    +----+----+
    |         |
    v         v
 Mobile    Web
 (Axios)   (SWR/fetch)
